"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-football-1895091-Aston-Villa-Olympiacos-Conference-League-medical-emergency\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The second half ofAston Villa'sEuropa Conference Leaguesemi-final first leg was delayed after a fan at Villa Park suffered a cardiac arrest.Unai Emery'sside trailed their Greek opponents 2-1 at the break and had to wait in the tunnel until the referee was given the green light to restart play.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 173, \"end\": 178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.86734868036731, \"rank\": 0.15221412122793143, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Players warmed up in the tunnel after medics had rushed to the scene in the Holte End, with a delay in proceedings before the second half got underway.\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TNT Sport claim that the incident took place just on the half-time whistle and nearby supporters were removed from the area, as an alert on the tannoy read: \\\"Could all supporters clear Holte Lower L2 and make sure the gangways are clear.\\\"\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TNT\", \"score\": 0.9994164954581339, \"rank\": 0.0004685927138739371, \"text\": \"TNT\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TNT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TNT\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As medics walked down the Holte End stairs with the person who suffered the cardiac arrest, both sets of fans applauded and the public announcer added: \\\"We'd like to thank the medical staff for their prompt assistance this evening.\\\"\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 717, \"end\": 726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Villa_Park\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Holte End\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Villa_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Villa_Park\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch all the Premier League and Champions League dramaunfold on TNT Sports    TNT host Jules Breach confirmed that the fan had suffered a cardiac arrest in the stands: \\\"Just to let you know, the reason that the second half has not got underway yet is because there has been a medical emergency in the stands, and there was a sign that went up just behind us that said to clear the lower Holte L2 area.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 958, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4580835934257379e-39, \"text\": \"Champions League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\"}, {\"begin\": 990, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1278230628403325e-19, \"text\": \"TNT Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TNT\", \"score\": 0.9994164954581339, \"rank\": 0.0004685927138739371, \"text\": \"TNT\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TNT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TNT\"}, {\"begin\": 1019, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breach_of_contract\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7081326063839688e-24, \"text\": \"Breach\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breach_of_contract\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breach_of_contract\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has now been cleared of all the fans, but there has been a cardiac arrest, and we are hearing that there is going to be a short delay to the second half.\\\"\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Ex-Premier League referee Halsey tears into Pawson after angering Chelsea stars  Do not miss:Chelsea star puts Todd Boehly in awkward spot in ongoing Pochettino 'dispute'  Do not miss:Palmer in angry confrontation with Chelsea coach after controversial Villa draw  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1567, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1221701820841788e-15, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1221701820841788e-15, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1612, \"end\": 1623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Boehly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Todd Boehly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Boehly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Boehly\"}, {\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauricio_Pochettino\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pochettino\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauricio_Pochettino\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauricio_Pochettino\"}, {\"begin\": 1720, \"end\": 1727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1221701820841788e-15, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  The second-half of Aston Villa vs Olympiacos is delayed due to a medical emergency in the crowd.More on this from@julesbreachand@Becky_Ives_...#UECL??????\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2029, \"end\": 2040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.364785130042939e-21, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2044, \"end\": 2054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.999999999917236, \"rank\": 8.261615168390317e-11, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"@tntsports&@discoveryplusUKpic.twitter.com/HKfbfcATDa  TNT Sports reporter Becky Ives then explained the situation further while pitchside.\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2219, \"end\": 2229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1278230628403325e-19, \"text\": \"TNT Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unfortunately right on the stroke of half-time the medical emergency happened,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was down the tunnel and the emergency services moved very quickly.\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2464, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They moved quickly to remove fans from the lower tier of the Holte End on the left hand side.\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been quite a few discussions going on as to how long the game will have to be halted for as the fan is moved into the waiting ambulance.\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2708, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously we wish the fan all our good wishes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympiacos enjoyed a surprise lead at half-time thanks to two goals from Ayoub El Kaabi, beforeOllie Watkinsgot a goal back before the break.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2758, \"end\": 2768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.999999999917236, \"rank\": 8.261615168390317e-11, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2831, \"end\": 2845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ayoub El Kaabi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moussa Diaby equalised after play had resumed, but El Kaabi completed his hat-trick from the penalty spot and Santiago Hezze's deflected effort made matters worse for Villa in Europe.\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 3084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2901, \"end\": 2913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moussa Diaby\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\"}, {\"begin\": 3011, \"end\": 3019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"score\": 0.9986015368485174, \"rank\": 0.0012147927409699507, \"text\": \"Santiago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3223, \"end\": 3236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7200650882715175e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3272, \"end\": 3285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7200650882715175e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"